{
  "title": "Uplifting Indian Kidney Bean Chaat",
  "description": "A bright, tangy chaat featuring smoky deep‑fried agemono, low‑sodium kidney beans, fresh herbs, and a splash of lemon for a romantic twist.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
