  "instructions": [
    "Heat a non‑stick skillet over medium heat and coat the agemono batter in a thin layer of oil.",
    "Add the agemono batter to the skillet and deep‑fry until golden and crispy, about 2 minutes per side, then transfer to paper towels to drain excess oil.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cooked kidney beans, diced cucumber, diced tomato, chopped coriander, and mint.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice over the bean mixture and toss gently to coat.",
    "Sprinkle the roasted cumin powder, chaat masala, black pepper, and optional sugar over the salad and mix again.",
    "Serve the crispy agemono pieces on top of the bean mixture, allowing the heat to release a subtle smoky aroma.",
    "Finish with a final squeeze of lemon, and serve immediately as a fresh, uplifting snack."
  ],
